<p>How can I make PHPStorm to use always the <code>phpunit.xml</code> in a project's directory by default.</p>  <p>The variable <code>{PROJECT_DIRECTORY}</code> is not working (was only guessed)</p>  <p>Click Path: Default Settings -> Languages &amp; Frameworks -> PHP -> PHP Unit</p>  <p><a href="http://i.stack.imgur.com/oG591.png" rel="nofollow"><img src="http://i.stack.imgur.com/oG591.png" alt="Screen"></a></p>  <p><em>edit</em> @LazyOne commented, that the path is automatically translated. But it is not:</p>  <ul> <li>Edited the default settings in some project A, select <code>phpunit.xml</code> from that project</li> <li>Opened another project</li> <li>Checked Default Settings</li> <li>The path of "some project A" is used</li> </ul>